{"tid":2225062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來呢個世界有啲咁既人","createTime":"2020-10-01T04:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T05:05:17.000Z","uid":146125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97ad03d008203fe324e536ee717984430e9030a0","tid":2225062,"uid":146125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱去IKEA個小食區個到買野食,聽到個肥婆同佢朋友既對話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=肥婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=佢朋友<br />\n話說佢地嗌咗2杯乳酪雪榚一人一杯<br />\n肥婆(望左望朋友杯雪榚):點解佢杯雪榚多過我個杯架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n職員:ERRR.....一係我比多啲你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥婆:好呀,快啲<br />\n跟住佢同個朋友講話<br />\n肥婆:都唔明點解你多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友:......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係隔離睇到O撚左,原來呢個世界真係有呢啲人存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed38db6c84b3857f1fc0b4775d048c33e1a2e153","tid":2225062,"uid":211878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb601c0207555fd66e1ff1fc925e5690de797e3","tid":2225062,"uid":146125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}